channel.title: Debate: why davidi2 should not get any more rep
channel.description:
I have nothing against him.I dont not want him to recieve rep or anything. he is an awesome guy and all. but there is 1 main reason.
If any idiot changes them then i will fuck them till king kong comes home.
Ok it is at "126". 126 is an amazing number. we all know it was the max stat leven in rs.
I really like david and he deserves to have some good reputation for having a good reputation number.
Bill
